::Feline::

She smiled at him. "Thank you...Honey." She chuckled slightly. "I"m 
going to have to get used to that."  She brought over a few leg parts 
and some wires and set them out on the table in front of him."See if 
you can't put tis leg together.  It's a bit large, but it may be 
needed.  I have to finish working on these joints and boards over 
here."  She kissed him tenderly,"  hmmm, Thank you again."

She walked over to the bench and started soldering wires and joints 
together.
